# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Smart Habit Tracker — Environment Variables
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Copy this file to `.env.local` and fill in the values, and also add the
# same values to your Vercel project (Settings → Environment Variables).
#
# ── A6 (Authentication + cloud data) — REQUIRED for sign-in & cloud sync ──
# From your Supabase project: Settings → API. See docs/Supabase-Setup.md.
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=
#
# Notes:
# - The anon key is a public, browser-safe key (protected by Row Level
#   Security). Do NOT put the service_role key here.
# - When these ARE set: the app requires login and stores each user's habit
#   data in Supabase (scoped per user via RLS).
# - When these are NOT set: the app runs in local mode (no login), storing
#   data in the browser's localStorage — the Gate 1 behaviour.
